{"tid":2062850,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李碧華 #名采","createTime":"2020-06-13T12:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:30:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"249e559bedeb2b7b63270304ea6a1e311dc21c88","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"李碧華 #名采<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200613/20936293/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200613%2F20936293%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=7f00e6a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200613%2F20936293%2F&h=562a27c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200613/20936293/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n窒息紅口罩 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200613/large/1591941021_923a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200613%2Flarge%2F1591941021_923a.jpg&h=734a2b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那天我約了人在地鐵站交收物品，旁邊有個男生也在等人，他把口罩扯開，打了兩個噴嚏，又咳起來。一瞧，是林鄭那底褲銅芯口罩呢。我們根本就不要，市面上也少見人戴。問：「小朋友你不舒服嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「這個口罩戴了好焗，好多立雜灰塵咁，咳都唔係第一次。」<br />\n<br />\n「那你除下，我給你一個新的吧，我有多。」<br />\n<br />\n他推辭，說等婆婆來接吃飯，入屋可除。<br />\n<br />\n「但你可告訴爸媽這口罩不舒服呀，上網一查就知有問題。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭虛應派送口罩，花了8億公帑，黑箱作業利益輸送，其防疫效能成疑，銅粒子還影響肺部健康，醫院明令禁戴。<br />\n<br />\n「我阿爸阿媽。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，如果升中大個仔了，更懂多方面思考。<br />\n<br />\n記得月前有11歲中一男生參加集會，他道：「我唔想咁細個就冇咗香港。」──但香港已經冇咗了！把子女送澳洲留學的偽教育局長楊潤雄，已出信逼校方唱好國安惡法，師生違者得進行政治紀律處分&hellip;&hellip;是個令人窒息的紅口罩。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"ea859c49a11059efca8499a7d058f9ee5398929d","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200614/20936913/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200614%2F20936913%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=1f079214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200614%2F20936913%2F&h=ddb35b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200614/20936913/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新興「地攤女友」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200614/large/1592031066_8172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200614%2Flarge%2F1592031066_8172.jpg&h=758c28cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫下，中共習李鬥矛盾白熱化，因為「地攤經濟」之爭議。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「說實話的代價」從來莫測，也分不清誰打了誰的臉，衝擊和迴響不絕。<br />\n<br />\n港人對此沒什麼關注，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，有些地攤卻相當吸睛。<br />\n<br />\n北京當局明確表示地攤經濟不適合首都，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，還有「地攤女友」招客。<br />\n<br />\n「女友」服務包括做家務、散步、打遊戲、聊天、看電影、牽手、聚會、逛街、陪喝酒、歌舞、親親、擁抱&hellip;&hellip;收2至20元人民幣不等，有套餐有包月，有單人匹馬也有「起雙飛」買一送一姊妹淘，任人觀賞瀏覽拍照，百貨應百客，街頭招徠不一定寫得很白，服務可商談價錢可另議。<br />\n<br />\n以前喚「企街」，如今是「坐街」，亦經濟發展一途。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"9bb8753b7c0f28fdcafd30d6e0ef701799a9a7b2","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200617/20938547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938547%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=94e1f38f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938547%2F&h=d6b5317d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200617/20938547/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n可能是「最後」了？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200617/large/1592296113_64c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200617%2Flarge%2F1592296113_64c8.jpg&h=30146fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武肺肆虐，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，時間甚為緊迫。<br />\n<br />\n籌備新書需時，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，所以此決策有點離地。<br />\n<br />\n希望多些來客？抑或量體溫戴口罩大家有距離的「限制入場」呢？如何消毒？人多了黑警「執法」嗎？──看來什麼「限聚令」，只針對示威者，雙重標準，司馬昭之心。往年每有逾百萬人入場，當局亦為了入場費吧？看到報導，出版社也特地提醒死線，所以還得趕工。<br />\n<br />\n以前我們並不很重視書展，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。明日陰晴未定，不管了。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"59226ed8b55d759cc8377a075eab39d221599c8f","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200619/20939880/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200619%2F20939880%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=04479c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200619%2F20939880%2F&h=75b119c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200619/20939880/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n天意和殺機 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200619/large/1592461951_a2a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200619%2Flarge%2F1592461951_a2a2.jpg&h=e1f336da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖開了幾個通宵趕工，還可以，不太累，靠意志力吧。與美術設計談封面，散會時已很晚，才開手機，充斥着「彩虹照」。<br />\n<br />\n整天都在忙，不知外頭世界。傍晚下過一場大雨後，竟出現兩條橫跨天際的雙彩虹，一條已是美景，還「兩條」，「雙」，不但罕見，且振奮人心，風雨過後，命不該絕，且添色彩。不止中環尖沙咀，全港多處包括東涌、大埔、沙田、深井、青馬大橋&hellip;&hellip;都有市民目睹奇景，還拍下來廣傳，即使不同地區角度，亦萬眾一心。<br />\n<br />\n看報導和評論：雙彩虹在東方文化中，象徵即將發生巨大的變革，也有人認為是吉兆，「變革」不一定負面，伏妖降魔重光也有彩虹作喻，天佑香港！<br />\n<br />\n雙彩虹沒殺傷力，。。。。。宇宙自然界有法則，也有天道，若天人合發生變革，亦天意，不怕，面對之。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"2e7e99630927653f76be73ec945ed474f2b11336","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200627/20944833/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200627%2F20944833%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=ffdf283d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200627%2F20944833%2F&h=7d54d43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200627/20944833/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n招魂認母 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200627/large/1593149670_b35b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200627%2Flarge%2F1593149670_b35b.jpg&h=b3108599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年9月底，15歲女生赤裸浮屍離奇出現在海面，警方指死因無可疑，且極速火化不留追查痕跡。死因裁判法庭近日就案件作研訊前檢討。<br />\n<br />\n死者是游泳健將陳彥霖，「自殺」抑「被自殺」一直充滿疑團。女兒失蹤，義助尋人的子明哥，在奔波期內知悉她死訊傳出，一夜之間與彥霖母親和舅父失去聯絡，兩位親人人間蒸發&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n彥霖曾多次參加反送中運動，花樣少女不明不白化作青灰，此後亦不少年輕人在示威抗爭中消失了，被送中被殺被自殺，成為空中飛人（落地無血）和海上浮屍，公安黑警暴行被包庇姑息，竟逍遙法外？為堵悠悠眾口，TVB新聞總監出馬做了陳母訪問，蒙面效果假得很；之後<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所以最好是包公審烏盆般招魂，一如Hello Kitty藏屍案開審時，法庭上所有光管不斷閃動，那被煮半熟的人頭自己申冤。亡魂庭上哭喊一聲：「媽！」，我們就信了。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1143323d89aae7a87725b375377c546da91b80b1","tid":2062850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200702/20947721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947721%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=7f1f6252\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947721%2F&h=36426d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200702/20947721/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n口紅妖（下） - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200702/large/1593584895_147b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200702%2Flarge%2F1593584895_147b.jpg&h=13adb58b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由中層主管爬上高層、最高層，是金字塔之路。<br />\n<br />\n工作很累，有時午<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n本就不討喜，怎能肩負重任？<br />\n<br />\n當她掏出那潘<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n──就像上電，連人也好看點。<br />\n<br />\n是的，這是<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n只是「藍蘋」。<br />\n<br />\n「。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n每回她元氣大傷又腹背受敵時，只消塗上這詭異的口紅，就換來一段時間的攀爬上進，贏得位高權重之驕傲，付出代價包括友情、親情、愛情和人緣──沒有朋友，六親緣薄，僅有的窩囊丈夫也受不了離婚了，子女隨父，而且在大機構中無一下屬信服只在淫威下陽奉陰違&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n殘餘的口紅快用完待添了，只能省着挖出來刮出來，薄薄塗一層──瞅着自己像個等待毒品的道姑，臉容扭曲肌肉抽搐，嘴唇乾澀而且思考能力遲鈍，一個字：「殘」！<br />\n<br />\n口紅妖出現時，林莎莉以為又可議價續期，提出僅存之籌碼：<br />\n<br />\n「我已付出生命中珍貴的東西了，怎能臨尾斷供？我還有高價的『尊嚴』&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈！」口紅妖笑：「這東西最不值錢了！而且你一早已失掉，竟然不曉 ？」<br />\n<br />\n丹祺口紅隨妖他去。永遠另有 買家。（完） <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com[/quote]"}]}